name: Strike of the Monarchs
effectText: Tribute 1 face-up Level 5 or higher Normal Summoned/Set monster, then target 1 face-up card on the field; negate its effects (until the end of this turn), then draw 1 card. During your Main Phase, if this card is in your GY: You can banish this card, then declare 1 Attribute; all face-up monsters currently on the field become that Attribute until the end of this turn.
